AnyDesk sesstion break when LID closed for Lenovo Legion 5i
-------------------------------------------------------------

Open Device Manager
Expand System Devices 
Right-Click ACPI Lid
Click on Properties 
Click on Driver 
Click on Update Driver 
Click on Browse my comptuer for Driver Software 
Click on Let me pick from a list of available drivers on my computer 
Uncheck Show Compatible Hardware 
Click on Standard Display Types 
Click on Microsoft Basic Display Driver
Hit next, okay, whatever until it's finished
